   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Open Microsoft Word.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Insert</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>My Add-ins</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Choose <uicontrol>Apttus X-Author</uicontrol> from the list of add-ins displayed in
               the drop-down. </p>
            <stepresult>
               <p>Apttus X-Author loads in a new pane to the right of the document window.</p>
